description: Before worlds collide, let’s round up all of our Bombshells and see where we’ve left off with each one: Miri Marvel and Mera, Poison Ivy and Harley Quinn, Zatanna and Raven, Batwoman, Vixen and Catwoman, and even Lois Lane, Killer Frost and the Reaper make their way into Russia to find Hugo Strange.
name: All Good Things Part 1 of 3

description: Translates Marvel Team-Up #51-52 & Marvel Team-Up Annual #3.

This zombie laced issue brings us face to face with modern terrors. Sometimes things are not always what they seem! Meet a Zombie that wants to die and a woman with a plan for the end of the world! The endings might just surprise you!
